18:32.876 --> 18:34.677
(laughing)

18:34.711 --> 18:37.280
That's why you give
toys to everyone,

18:37.314 --> 18:38.848
whether they're
naughty or nice.

18:38.882 --> 18:40.950
The naughty kids
buy the most toys.

18:40.984 --> 18:42.051
