I'm proud of you, son.

19:26.830 --> 19:28.698
You're a good guy.

19:28.732 --> 19:29.799
Because of you.

19:29.833 --> 19:31.367
Because you were so hard on me.

19:31.401 --> 19:32.668
Maybe.

