20:12.776 --> 20:14.510
(grunts)

20:17.347 --> 20:19.682
You're...
Krampus.

20:19.716 --> 20:21.183
So I am.

20:21.218 --> 20:24.687
I suppose this is how I'm
to repay my debt to the world

20:24.721 --> 20:27.390
for taking Krampus away
all these years.

20:27.424 --> 20:29.592
So, will you remain
Krampus forever?

20:29.626 --> 20:30.926
Like, all the time?

20:30.961 --> 20:32.261
Who knows?

20:32.295 --> 20:34.029
In the meantime,
it's Christmas Eve,

20:34.064 --> 20:37.299
and I've got a lot
of bottoms to blister.

20:37.334 --> 20:39.935
